	<h1 class="story-header">Meat feast: Is it time to change the way we eat meat?</h1>

     
         
 
        
    		
					            	    		 			<span class="byline">
														<span class="byline-name">By Anna-Louise Taylor</span>
				<span class="byline-title">BBC Food</span>
			</span>
		        
        <div class="caption body-width">
  <img src="http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/68845000/jpg/_68845469_roast_leg_of_lamb_with_02393_16x9.jpg" width="464" height="261" alt="Roast lamb " />

    <span style="width:464px;">Should we be making more of a special cut - only on certain days?</span>
  </div>
